      • isApptTimesAllowedAgainstList

        public static boolean isApptTimesAllowedAgainstList​(javafx.collections.ObservableList<Appointments> apptList,
                                                    Appointments test,
                                                    Appointments oneToEdit)
        Checks if appointment is allowed to be added against list and possible edited appointment
        Parameters:
        apptList - list of appointments
        test - appointment to be added
        oneToEdit - appointment to be edited (can be NULL)
        Returns:
        true if appointment is allowed

        ***LAMBDA USAGE BELOW #1***

        Lambda usage in code in order to set new Predicate on filtered list to not include the edited appointment as long as the test appointment is not equal to the edited one.
